title: ImportError: cannot import name caffe2_pb2
body_html:
Issue description

I have compiled the latest versions of PyTorch, ONNX, and Caffe2, all from source.

When I enter

import caffe2.python.onnx.backend

I get the following error messages:

Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "<stdin>", line 1, in <module>
  File "pytorch/caffe2/python/onnx/backend.py", line 26, in <module>
    from caffe2.python import core, workspace, rnn_cell, gru_cell
  File "pytorch/caffe2/python/core.py", line 14, in <module>
    from caffe2.proto import caffe2_pb2
ImportError: cannot import name caffe2_pb2

Collecting environment information...
PyTorch version: 0.5.0a0+d154d32
Is debug build: No
